the left. e, Histogram of the B-factor values of all non-hydrogen atoms in the atomic model, coloured by the same colour key in d. f, Model-map FSC. g, Focused classification and refinement of the GR-loading complex. Masks were created at various regions of the GR-loading complex (left) and its corresponding gold-standard FSC (right) after 3D auto-refine. The nominal resolution for each reconstruction is labelled and indicated in the FSC plots.

